  "texts": [
    "The authenticity and diversity of these reviews stem from real user contributions on the movie website, enhancing the datasets' representativeness.",
    "• Sentiment140 (Go et al, 2009).",
    "Derived from tweet contents on Twitter, the Sentiment140 dataset consists of tweets labeled with positive or negative sentiment.",
    "The data is curated by the creator through API calls, filtering tweets from diverse domains such as consumer products, companies, individuals, and others, based on their content.",
    "• SST-2 (Socher et al, 2013)."
  ]
